Package com.adobe.creativesdk.foundation.storage

Contains classes for working with assets and libraries in Creative Cloud.

See: Description

    IAdobeGenericRequestCallback is a generic interface for providing callback in case of a request completion, error, progress or cancel events.

    The generic completion handler for asynchronous and order-based listing of photo assets.

    IAdobeRequestCompletionCallback is a generic interface for providing callback when a user request completes.
